---
title: Bistro Steak with Mushrooms & Polenta Cakes plus Roasted Green Beans
description: Meat and polenta is the new meat and potatoes in this steakhouse-worthy meal. Bavette steak is cooked to juicy perfection and served alongside oven-roasted green beans and golden,  Parmesan polenta. Top it all off with an umami-packed mushroom-crème fraîche sauce for a show-stopping dinner everyone will love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65f0b9ddf15f35246a8cb4fa-a7fe7fb4.jpeg
